parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dim or Inadequate Low Beam Headlights
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Insufficient low beam headlights can significantly impair nighttime visibility, increasing the risk of accidents and compromising driver safety.
symptoms: Low beam headlights are dim or weak
making it difficult to see the road at night
requiring frequent use of high beams
and reducing overall nighttime driving safety.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Slipping or Jumping into Neutral
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or jumping into neutral can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and damage to the transmission, leading to costly repairs.
symptoms: The transmission slips or jumps into neutral while driving
the vehicle hesitates or stutters when shifting gears
the vehicle is stuck in low gear
the vehicle has difficulty shifting into higher gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty transmission control module can cause intermittent transmission problems, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and damage to the transmission.
symptoms: Intermittent transmission problems
transmission slips or jumps into neutral
transmission hesitates or stutters when shifting gears
other vehicle systems malfunction intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the weather stripping can cause water to leak into the vehicle, leading to damage to electrical components, carpets, and upholstery, and potentially causing safety issues such as short circuits or slippery floors.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle
water spots or stains on carpets or upholstery
musty odor inside the vehicle
rust or corrosion on metal components
electrical issues or short circuits.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Air Conditioner Hose Leak at O-Rings
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The leakage of refrigerant from the air conditioner hose can cause the air conditioning system to malfunction, leading to reduced cooling performance, increased fuel consumption, and potential damage to other components.
symptoms: The air conditioning system blows warm air
the air conditioning system is not cooling properly
refrigerant leaks are visible
the vehicle's fuel efficiency decreases.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handle can cause difficulty or impossibility in opening or closing the door, which can lead to inconvenience, safety risks, and potential entrapment.
symptoms: The door handle breaks or cracks
the door handle feels loose or wobbly
the door handle does not latch properly
the door handle is difficult to operate
the door does not open or close properly.
